The caculator gui tree

---------------------------Frame---------------------------
                   |                        |
-----------------Output-----------------Main Panel----------
									  |					|							
--------------------------------Button Panel----------Button

The button panel uses the grid layout manager of 4 by 4
The button uses no layout manager because its a button

The button panel and button will both be added to the main panel the main panel uses the borderBox layout
The button panel would be added to the middle
The button would be added  to the south

The output would a JTextArea which is not editable
The output and main panel would be added to the panel which is the frames content pane
This panel would have a box layout of vertical 

